room_title: Escape room "Seance" by Stumptown Escape Games in Portland
review: My wife and I came here and did the Seance room on our 7th anniversary. It was just the 2 of us in the room and we had an absolute blast. Sooo much fun, and we solved it with 52.59 seconds remaining. Great staff, great place, and we're definitely going back.
